1
00:00:38,160 --> 00:00:39,720
So we need to think of a way

2
00:00:40,480 --> 00:00:42,200
to make them kill each other.

3
00:00:43,920 --> 00:00:44,980
Do you have an idea?

4
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:49,080
Anyway,

5
00:00:50,120 --> 00:00:53,450
Angwei is currently protecting me more than suspecting me.

6
00:00:53,640 --> 00:00:55,560
But we can use this incident

7
00:00:56,080 --> 00:00:57,680
to see his motives clearly.

8
00:00:58,400 --> 00:00:59,530
If he can protect me,

9
00:01:00,480 --> 00:01:02,810
it means this knife is already in my hands.

10
00:01:04,040 --> 00:01:04,800
Which means it's a good time

11
00:01:04,800 --> 00:01:06,840
to make them kill each other.

12
00:01:07,840 --> 00:01:09,120
Besides, Ou Shaowen

13
00:01:09,520 --> 00:01:11,380
also wants to get the Laiao Route.

14
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:15,210
He will definitely be willing to lend us some forces.

15
00:01:15,360 --> 00:01:18,220
We can just use them to suppress Danpa and Ruannila.

16
00:01:20,520 --> 00:01:21,760
Leave that killer to me.

17
00:01:21,760 --> 00:01:24,000
He saw me. I have to shut him up.

18
00:01:26,160 --> 00:01:26,880
Stay safe.

19
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:46,500
Don't move.

20
00:01:56,080 --> 00:01:57,039
Who sent you?

21
00:01:57,800 --> 00:01:58,920
Ruannila or Danpa?

22
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:28,800
Angwei?

23
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:31,050
Why are you here?

24
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:39,400
The killer sent to Dailing's room tonight,

25
00:02:40,240 --> 00:02:41,770
you hired them, didn't you?

26
00:02:42,040 --> 00:02:42,840
Killer?

27
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:45,280
I don't know anything about it.

28
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,320
She is mine.

29
00:02:48,600 --> 00:02:49,600
If you touch her,

30
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:51,840
I will kill you.

31
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:11,640
Sir.

32
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:13,800
The bullet in the assassin's head

33
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:14,860
has been taken out.

34
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:16,880
The model is a special bullet for a British pistol.

35
00:03:16,880 --> 00:03:19,000
It's rarely circulated on the market.

36
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,260
Only a few mercenaries

37
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:22,120
can get it through special channels.

38
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:22,760
So,

39
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:25,480
the female assassin is a mercenary.

40
00:03:27,480 --> 00:03:28,160
Go check

41
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:30,320
the list of mercenaries in the border city five years ago.

42
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:31,760
Get me the files of all the female mercenaries

43
00:03:31,760 --> 00:03:33,020
who suddenly retired.

44
00:03:50,880 --> 00:03:51,740
Hello, Father.

45
00:03:52,040 --> 00:03:52,640
Angwei,

46
00:03:53,079 --> 00:03:54,040
I have a document here

47
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:55,680
sent from Nanyang.

48
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:58,160
Deliver it personally

49
00:03:58,160 --> 00:04:00,320
to Mr. Zhang in the suburbs.

50
00:04:00,920 --> 00:04:01,720
This concerns

51
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:04,120
the interests of our Sihai Group.

52
00:04:04,600 --> 00:04:06,260
You must deliver it yourself.

53
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:23,000
Where are you?

54
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:26,290
Send me the address. I'll come pick you up.

55
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:35,210
A thief broke into Ang Wei's house yesterday.

56
00:04:37,400 --> 00:04:38,280
Are you hurt?

57
00:04:44,640 --> 00:04:45,600
How did you know?

58
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,880
I just happened to pass by yesterday

59
00:04:48,880 --> 00:04:49,880
and saw the thief.

60
00:04:50,640 --> 00:04:53,170
I was just about to ask who the mastermind was,

61
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:54,440
but he was shot dead.

62
00:04:56,080 --> 00:04:58,010
I checked the nearby surveillance

63
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:01,660
and captured this person's back.

64
00:05:08,320 --> 00:05:09,180
Do you know her?

65
00:05:10,280 --> 00:05:11,610
She's from my hometown.

66
00:05:13,280 --> 00:05:14,810
Do you know her background?

67
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:16,640
Making friends.

68
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:18,170
Why talk about background?

69
00:05:18,440 --> 00:05:19,280
But I'm sure

70
00:05:19,840 --> 00:05:21,240
Sister Hua won't harm me.

71
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:24,300
I didn't mean that.

72
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,440
I just think she

73
00:05:28,840 --> 00:05:29,880
is a bit strange.

74
00:05:31,200 --> 00:05:32,460
After investigation,

75
00:05:34,280 --> 00:05:34,880
Feifei.

76
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:39,370
Let's go.

77
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:41,010
Come with me to the suburbs.

78
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:00,920
What's wrong, Young Master?

79
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:02,250
Didn't the talk go well?

80
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,040
Stop talking.

81
00:06:07,360 --> 00:06:08,620
Just focus on driving.

82
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:15,800
What did you just talk about with Ou Shaowen?

83
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:17,330
Nothing much to talk about.

84
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:19,220
We are just ordinary friends.

85
00:06:41,280 --> 00:06:42,540
You like butterflies?

86
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:45,640
Although they are small,

87
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:49,000
they can break through the cocoon and be reborn,

88
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,659
and fly across the wide ocean.

89
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:05,520
Is it this butterfly?

90
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:37,860
I'll get out and check.

91
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:13,800
Dailing.
